Several target performances of the proposed muscle-like actuator are determined for the wearable robot application. The actuator should be designed to produce high force in the desired deformation range. As preloading the SMA is required to be stretched, the target range of deformation is determined under load conditions. The target force required is 10 N per a single coil spring. The target maximum contraction ratio is selected to be greater than 40% of its initial stretched length, which exhibits a similar contraction ratio as that of a human muscle [60]. The target displacement range is selected as 50 mm Afrpoplm. Sciit.s20in19i,ti9a, lx sFtOreRtPchEEeRdRleEnVgIEtWh when a 10 N load is applied to the spring samples. Target max5imofu1m5 tloenthgtehsopfritnhge sspamrinpgleiss. sTealregcetetdmuapxitmo u15m0 lmenmg,thwohficthheissapsriunigtaibslesesliezcetefodruapcotom1p5a0ctmwmea, rwabhliechroibs oat sfuoirtathbelewsirziestf.oIrnaacdodmitpioanct, wa emaarainblceornosbiodtefroartitohneiwn raicstt.uIantoardddeitsiiognn, aismthaaint tchoensaicdtueraattoironshinoualcdtubaetoars dtheisnigansipsothssaitbtlheetoacmtuaakteorthsehowueladrabbelaesrtohbiontapsoprotasbslieblaentdo meaaskyetothwe ewaer.aFrainbalellryo, bthoet pmoarxtaimbluemansdurefaascye ttoemwpeearra. tFuirneahllays, tthoebme aasxliomwumas spuorsfsaicbeletetomppreervaetuntrebuhransintogboef ahsumloawnasskipnossisnibcelethtoe pSMrevAeinstabcutirvnaitnegd obfyhtuhme ianncrsekainsesoinfcteemthpeeSraMtuArei.s activated by the increase of temperature.
