The fabricated SMA-based actuator is shown in Figure 5. The SMA-based actuator shows high stretchability. It can contract and release 40% of its initial stretched length with an actuation frequency of 0.5 Hz when 1 kg pre-load is applied. Since the average frequency responses of general ADLs is around 1 Hz [61], the proposed actuator can support the ADLs of low frequencies. The SMA coil

