smaller. Additionally, the actuator has to be heated to a higher temperature to exert high force

compared to other samples. Sample 1, 2 shows enough force over 10 N, but it needs larger

displacement range than the target value. The optimal SMA coil spring is selected as sample 3 since

it satisfies the target force in the displacement range, is the thinnest, and has the lowest transition

temperature.

